{"word":"φοιταλέος","slug":"φοιταλέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φοιταλέος</b></el> <el>(φοιτᾰλέος, η, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φοιτάω'><el>φοιτάω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>roaming wildly about</i>, <b><a href='S:Moschus'>Mosch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>driving madly about, maddening</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}